(42, 9, 33, 19, 4, 6, 7, 'it is good for us to be here', 'Gladness and Presence of God', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine presence and joy. In Luke, Peter expresses a desire to remain in the presence of Jesus, while in Psalms, the psalmist seeks the Lord''s countenance to experience gladness.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
